These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, adventure
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, vegafina
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold
2 different games are played: poker, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, october
House: cape-cod, victorian
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, orange
1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
2. the victorian house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
5. the person who likes orange is the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person playing backgammon is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Movie-Genre      | adventure        | comedy |
| Cigar          | vegafina  | bluemaster     |
| Flower         | marigold    | lily         |
| Game           | poker    | backgammon |
| Birthday   | december  | october     |
| House           | victorian      | cape-cod    |
| Color         | orange | blood-red          |

