.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, lime
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda
City: new-york, marseilles
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry
2 different games are played: scrabble, chess
House: cottage, art-deco
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, orchid
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Food         | apple      | lime       |
| Beverage           | lemonade | mirinda |
| City   | marseilles      | new-york        |
| Cigar   | bongani         | old-henry        |
| Game   | scrabble    | chess       |
| House           | art-deco        | cottage          |
| Flower     | orchid          | sunflower    |

